snippet.title: Faraway: Puzzle Escape - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Faraway is a puzzle adventure game, a modern tribute to Myst designed for phones and tablets. Read more at http://www.farawaygame.com/
Android: https://goo.gl/n8rsrM 
iOS: https://goo.gl/aRv1T8 

Made by Pine Studio - 2017
